    <h1 class="rdigest">The RISKS Digest</h1>
    <h1 class="cntr">Forum on Risks to the Public in Computers and Related Systems</h1>
    <h2 class="cntr">
	<i><a href="//www.acm.org">ACM</a> Committee on Computers and Public Policy,
	<a href="http://www.csl.sri.com/neumann/neumann.html">Peter G. Neumann</a>, moderator</i>
    </h2>
    <h2 class="cntr">Volume 31 Issue 08</h2>
        <h2 class="cntr">Tuesday 26 February 2019</h2><h2>Contents</h2><dl>
<dt><i class="circle fas fa-circle"></i>
<a href="#subj1">Lion Air Crash Fixes Delayed</a></dt>
<dd><a href="#subj1.1">WSJ</a><br/>
</dd><dt><i class="circle fas fa-circle"></i>
<a href="#subj2">Setback for Israeli lunar lander as computer glitch prevents scheduled  maneuver</a></dt>
<dd><a href="#subj2.1">The Times of Israel</a><br/>
</dd><dt><i class="circle fas fa-circle"></i>
