<dd><a href="#subj8.1">ThreatPost</a><br/>
</dd><dt><i class="circle fas fa-circle"></i>
<a href="#subj9">Rabbit Holes that, by simply choosing not to do Internet video, we have  Not Gone Down</a></dt>
<dd><a href="#subj9.1">NYTimes</a><br/>
</dd><dt><i class="circle fas fa-circle"></i>
<a href="#subj10">... but we &quot;never activated the cameras&quot;</a></dt>
