Gabe Goldberg 
&lt;gabe@gabegold.com&gt;
</address>
<i>Fri, 8 Mar 2019 16:25:07 -0500</i><pre>
Is Your Seatmate Googling You? (NYTimes)
We underestimate the risks to privacy in our everyday, offline lives.
Read More... &lt;<a href="https://nyti.ms/2UrV2NE?smid=nytcore-ios-share">https://nyti.ms/2UrV2NE?smid=nytcore-ios-share</a>&gt;

</pre>

